-ionisation wake (mainly) and an accretion wake (secondarily) are\nresponsible for the orbital evolution of the absorption column, the continuum\nemission and the variability seen at the Fe-line complex.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Dec 2020 19:38:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
