 research,\nexperimentation and simulation, and a related focus on evaluative approaches,\nall suggest that existing tools, methods and approaches from related fields are\nbeing tested in the GSE context, even though these may not be inherently\napplicable to the additional scale and complexity of GSE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2020 00:03:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-01"}
