 process\nplacement approach in Slurm, the reduction is 18.9% and 31%, respectively for\ntwo different MPI applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Dec 2020 14:09:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jan 2021 11:03:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
